Titolo: Lanota

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Lanota is an indie rhythm game developed and published by Noxy Games. The iOS version and the Android version were both released globally on the App Store and the Google Play Store respectively on July 13, 2016. The game on iOS requires initial purchase, but the Android version allows free play up to Chapter 3, interspersed with ads. On April 13, 2018, it was announced that a Switch port of Lanota by Flyhigh Works was undergoing development. The port was released worldwide in June 2018.Lanota includes a story told in a picture book style, map exploration, and item collecting along with the main rhythm game gameplay. Players must complete songs in order to advance the story and unlock more songs.

Genere: Music 

Valutazione: 72
